### 视图管理接口

@baseUrl = http://localhost

### 创建视图管理
POST {{baseUrl}}/workspace/view
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "我的视图",
  "type": "list",
  "spaceId": 1,
  "ownerId": 1,
  "isPublic": 0,
  "config": "{}"
}

### 更新视图管理
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workspace/view/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新后的视图名称",
  "type": "kanban",
  "config": "{\"columns\": []}"
}

### 删除视图管理
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workspace/view/1

### 根据ID查询视图管理
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspace/view/1

### 查询视图管理列表（不含文件夹结构）
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspace/view/list

### 查询视图树形列表（包含文件夹和视图的树形结构）
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspace/view/tree-list

### 分页查询视图管理
POST {{baseUrl}}/workspace/view/page
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "spaceId": null,
  "folderId": null,
  "type": "",
  "ownerId": null,
  "isPublic": null,
  "keyword": ""
}

